NAME

DateTime::Locale::km_KH - Locale data examples for the Khmer Cambodia (km-KH) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Khmer Cambodia locale.

Datetime Formats

Full

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = សុក្រ 22 ធ្នូ 1995 នៅ​ម៉ោង 9:05:02 AM UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = សៅរ៍ 15 កញ្ញា -10 នៅ​ម៉ោង 4:44:23 AM UTC

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 ធ្នូ 1995, 9:05:02 AM
